            bindings = <
        &kp GRAVE  &kp N7        &kp N8        &kp N9        &kp LBRC    &kp RBRC  &kp EXCLAMATION       &kp AT_SIGN      &kp POUND               &kp DOLLAR
        &kp EQUAL  &kp NUMBER_4  &kp N5        &kp N6        &kp LBKT    &kp RBKT  &mt RIGHT_SHIFT PLUS  &mt RCTRL MINUS  &mt RIGHT_ALT ASTERISK  &mt RGUI SLASH
&trans  &kp N0     &kp NUMBER_1  &kp NUMBER_2  &kp NUMBER_3  &kp LPAR    &kp RPAR  &kp PERCENT           &kp CARET        &kp AMPERSAND           &kp PIPE        &trans
